Susan Matheson bụ onye na-emepụta ejiji nke mepụtara ejiji etiti n'ihe nkiri The Kingdom, Friday Night Lights, Blue Crush, Crazy/Beautiful, Honey, Panic na Best Laid Plans. O mepụtara ihe ehiri mee ihe nkiri atọ nke Will Ferrell - Step Brothers, Semi-Pro, na Talladega Nights: The Ballad of Ricky Bobby O meputakwara ihe ehiri mee ihe nkiri Couples Retreat nke Vince Vaughn na Jon Favreau gosipụtara nke mbụ ya n'oge mgbụsị akwụkwọ nke afọ 2009.

Susan Matheson tolitere na Cape Town, South Africa. Susan nwetara nzere bachelọ ya na Vassar College na BFA ya na Parsons School of Design ebe ọ natara onyinye ",onye mmepụta ihe oyiyi nke afọ" yana onyinye maka mmepụta ihe oyiyi site na Nike, Inc
na Bob Mackie. Mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ, ọ gara rụọ ọrụ na ụlọ ọrụ Mattel Toys na-emepụtara  Barbie na Disney.
Kemgbe ahụ, ọ gara n'ihu na-emepụta ejiji maka ihe nkiri na ejiji
Susan esorowo ndị na-eme ihe nkiri Ron Athey, Juliana Snapper na Nicole Blackman rụkọọ ọrụ

N'oge na-adịbeghị anya, ya na Juliana Snapper na onye na-ede egwu Andrew bụ Infanti rụkọtara ọrụ na ọnwa Mee afọ 2009 na omume opera mbụ n'okpuru mmiri "You will emerge from the flood" na Victoria Baths na Manchester, UK.
